Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:39.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:278570,279821}Katsuragi-san.{NOTE:桂城さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:42.36,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:279821,282365}Our basketball team is looking for promising newcomers.{NOTE:バスケット部は有望な新人を求めます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:282365,283825}Katsuragi-san!{NOTE:桂城さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.07,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:283825,285076}Ah, Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:あ、鮎原さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:47.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:285076,287788}Katsuragi-san, what are you doing at the basketball club?{NOTE:桂城さん、どうしてバスケット部何か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.37,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:287788,289372}You made it here, Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:来たわね、鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:51.29,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:289372,291291}What happened to volleyball, Senpai?{NOTE:先輩、バレーはどうしたんです？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.66,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:291291,292667}Did you quit?{NOTE:辞めたんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.50,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:292667,295504}Hmm. Things changed about six months ago.{NOTE:んん。半年ほど前に変わったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.33,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:295504,297339}Changed how?{NOTE:なぜですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:05:02.67,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:297339,302677}The volleyball club is dominated by the captain,\NOonuma Miyuki, and her followers.{NOTE:バレー部はね、大沼みゆきと言うキャプテンと、取り巻きグループが支配して…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:06.01,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:302677,306014}In order to keep their captain popular…{NOTE:…そのキャプテンの人気を保つためには…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:10.51,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:306014,310519}…her followers are trying to get any popular or skillful newcomers to quit.{NOTE:…取り巻き連中が実力のある人や人気者を追い出しにかかるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:310519,312312}They really do that?{NOTE:ま、追い出す？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:312312,314815}And the club's advisor just turns a blind eye to it?{NOTE:部長先生は黙ってらっしゃるんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.69,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:314815,317692}Professor Shimizu just has no control over her.{NOTE:んん。清水先生XXXきれないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.27,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:317692,319277}Professor Shimizu?{NOTE:清水先生？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.86,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:319277,320862}That woman teacher?{NOTE:あの女の先生ですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:21.73,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:320862,321738}Yes.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:24.53,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:321738,324533}I think a woman teacher is no good for a girls' team.{NOTE:女子チームにはやっぱり女の先生無理よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.70,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:324533,326701}She's too lenient.{NOTE:(XXX・ジンクス)だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.28,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:326701,329287}You should really consider entering the basketball club.{NOTE:ね。あなた達バスケット部へ入らない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.91,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:329287,331915}It'll be easy to adapt for someone who come from a volleyball club.{NOTE:バレー部からの転校しやすいと思うけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:36.12,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:333375,336127}I'm sorry, but I can't see myself doing anything but volleyball.{NOTE:ん、私はバレー以外は考えられないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.38,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:337254,338380}What about you?{NOTE:あなたは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:338380,340632}I feel the same way.{NOTE:私もバレーだけよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:43.59,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:340632,343593}I guess that's to be expected.{NOTE:そうね。あなた達に分かってもらえそうもないので。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:343593,345846}Well, I'll go check out the volleyball club now.{NOTE:ともかくバレー部へ行ってみます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.64,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:347305,348640}I'll go with her. See you later.{NOTE:私も失礼します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.35,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:352310,354354}Uhm, what should we do, Senpai?{NOTE:あの、どういうことなんですか、先輩？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:57.94,Default,Katsuragi,0,0,0,,{TIME:354354,357941}I guess you could stick around for a bit and see things for yourself.{NOTE:んあなた達は少し様子を見た方がいいわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.65,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:361152,363655}Isn't that the volleyball club's room?{NOTE:あそこがバレー部の部室じゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.07,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:365073,367075}– …right?\N– Hahaha.{NOTE:—でしょう？\\N—ははは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:09.91,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:369202,369911}Uhm…{NOTE:あの…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.91,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:371580,373915}Uhm, we'd like to enter your club…{NOTE:あの、私達入部希望のものですか。}
Comment: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:15.87,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:375083,375876}Fufu.{NOTE:ふふ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:17.33,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:375876,377335}Captain's not here.{NOTE:キャプテン不在だから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:19.42,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:377335,379421}We'll talk to you in her stead. What do you want?{NOTE:私達は話を聞くわ。何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.17,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:379421,381172}What are your names and classes?{NOTE:で、名前とクラスは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:24.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:381172,384134}I'm a first year, Ayuhara Kozue from group C.{NOTE:一年C組の鮎原こずえです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:26.38,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:384134,386386}I'm Hayakawa Midori from group A.{NOTE:私はA組の早川みどりです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:28.76,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:386970,388763}Hm? And your experience with volleyball?{NOTE:ん？バレーの経験は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:37.48,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:390807,397480}We both were Japanese representatives at Junior Volleyball World Championship.{NOTE:私達は二人共中学時代にジュニアバレー世界選手権の日本の代表メンバーでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.77,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:397480,400775}We asked you about your experience with volleyball!{NOTE:私達はね、バレーの経験があるかって聞いたんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:42.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:401943,402986}Midori.{NOTE:みどり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:44.02,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:402986,404029}But you can see…!{NOTE:だって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:47.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:404029,407073}We've played volleyball for three years at middle school.{NOTE:中学で三年間やってきました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:47.78,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:407073,407782}I see.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:48.65,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:407782,408658}That's neat.{NOTE:それは結構。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.74,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:408658,409743}But you see…{NOTE:でもね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:53.33,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:409743,413330}High school is different from children's games.{NOTE:高校は子供のボール遊びでは違うんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:54.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:413330,414372}Children's games?{NOTE:ボール遊び？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:07:00.17,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:415373,420170}Yeah, and it's definitely not the place to brag about your children's games either.{NOTE:それに、そのボール遊びを鼻にかけるような子供にも関係のないところなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:420170,421296}W-What…?{NOTE:そ、そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:03.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:421296,423590}We just want to play volleyball.{NOTE:私達はただバレーをやりたいだけです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:05.50,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:424174,425508}Really, now?{NOTE:そうかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:09.38,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:425508,429387}I think you want to be treated as a star,\Nlike you used to be during middle school, right?{NOTE:中学時代みたいにスター遣いされたいだけ何じゃないかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:429387,430472}That's not true!{NOTE:そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.51,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:430472,431514}Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.60,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:431514,434601}Let's talk directly with the captain\Nor Professor Shimizu.{NOTE:キャプテンか清水先生に直接話をしましょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.68,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:434601,435685}Hold on.{NOTE:ちょっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:18.43,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:435685,438438}We never said that we wouldn't let you join us.{NOTE:私達はあなた達は入れないって言ってるんじゃないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.19,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:438980,440190}Then what's with that talk?{NOTE:だったら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.31,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:440190,442317}There are conditions, though.{NOTE:条件があるんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.23,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:442317,444235}You could say it's our club's tradition.{NOTE:バレー部伝統のね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.23,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:444235,445236}Tradition?{NOTE:伝統？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:26.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:445236,446154}What kind?{NOTE:何ですか？}
Comment: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:26.98,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:446154,446988}Fufufu.{NOTE:ふふ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:28.53,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:447489,448531}Rule #1.{NOTE:一つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:31.20,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:448531,451201}Captain's orders are absolute.{NOTE:キャプテンの命令に絶対服従。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:31.95,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:451201,451952}Rule #2.{NOTE:二つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.99,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:451952,453995}Same goes to the seniors.{NOTE:先輩に対して同じく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:34.82,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:453995,454829}And the final rule…{NOTE:そして…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.99,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:454829,457999}You need to be polite at all times when you face your seniors. Got it?{NOTE:先輩全てに対して礼儀正しく。いいね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:38.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:457999,458541}Yes.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:42.25,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:459459,462253}Then clean the court right away.{NOTE:分かったら早速コートの掃除するんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:42.92,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:462253,462921}Yes ma'am!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:463338,464214}Midori.{NOTE:みどり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.13,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:467467,468134}What do you think?{NOTE:どう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:52.47,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:468134,472472}I guess these two are a bit different from the other freshmen.{NOTE:やっぱりあの二人は他の新入生とはちょっとばかり違うよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.84,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:472472,473848}This is bad.{NOTE:XXX不味いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.43,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:473848,476434}If we let them loose, they'll outshine us.{NOTE:期待すれば私達が霞んじゃうわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:08:00.35,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:476434,480355}Actually, it'll be easy. We just need to make it\Nso that they quit of their own accord.{NOTE:自分達から退部するように仕向けるんだ。簡単よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:03.60,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:480355,483608}That way, they can't hold us responsible for anything.{NOTE:そうすれば、誰の責任でもないってわけね。}
Comment: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:04.85,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:483608,484859}– Hahaha.\N– Fufu.{NOTE:—ははは。\\N—ふふ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.99,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:496788,498999}How long do you think they'll stay with us?{NOTE:あの子達どのくらい続くかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:21.91,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:499958,501918}I don't think it'll be too long before they leave.{NOTE:どうせ直ぐ逃げ出すのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.00,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:501918,504004}Then we'll get bullied all over again…{NOTE:そうしたら又私達はやらされるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:504921,506631}Ah, finally we're done.{NOTE:あ、やっと終わったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.75,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:506631,508758}Just look at those second-years.{NOTE:もう。あの二年生達ったら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.21,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:508758,510218}It wouldn't kill them to help us.{NOTE:手伝ったりいいのにね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.55,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:510218,512554}Why are you standing there doing nothing?{NOTE:何ぼやぼやしてるの！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:513054,514014}Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:38.43,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:514764,518435}You think you're done? The floor still needs to be polished to a shine with a dry rag.{NOTE:それが終わったら乾いた雑巾で乾拭きしなくちゃいけないんじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:39.72,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:518435,519728}Get started already!{NOTE:早く！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:41.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:519728,521062}Polished to a shine?{NOTE:乾拭き？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:45.56,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:521062,525567}It's our tradition decided by Captain Oonuma.{NOTE:それがここの伝統。大沼キャプテンの決めた掃除方法。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.65,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:525567,526651}Now get moving!{NOTE:ぐずぐずしないで！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:47.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:526651,527527}Y-Yes ma'am.{NOTE:は、はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:48.11,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:527527,528111}On it.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.79,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:546880,549799}Get started with your gymnastics!{NOTE:さ！あなた達は柔軟体操を始める！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:10.84,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:549799,550842}– Yes ma'am!\N– Yes ma'am!{NOTE:—はい！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.47,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:553053,554471}I won't give up.{NOTE:負けるもんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.47,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:556347,557474}Dammit.{NOTE:くそ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:28.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:567692,568777}Ah, we made it.{NOTE:あ、終わった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.73,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:569360,572739}This is too much. I feel like Cinderella.{NOTE:酷いわ。まるで嫁いびりじゃないの、これじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:573740,574324}Shh!{NOTE:シー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:36.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:574324,576534}Midori, the seniors are here.{NOTE:みどり、ほら。先輩が来たわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.87,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:578411,579871}Patch these up.{NOTE:これ、繕ってちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:581873,583374}T-These…?{NOTE:こ、これをですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:47.12,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:583374,587128}Captain Oonuma teaches us to respect the equipment.{NOTE:用具は大切に使って、大沼キャプテンが言われるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.25,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:587128,588254}Catch.{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:53.00,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:590465,593009}There's no way we can use that ball anymore.{NOTE:こんなボールもう使えられるしないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:58.89,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:596221,598890}Oopsie, I'm sorry for bumping into you.{NOTE:あら、ごめんなさい、XXちゃって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:09:59.80,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:598890,599808}Are you hurt?{NOTE:怪我なかった？}
