Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:57.80,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015890,1017808}Plus it's them who wanted that match.{NOTE:それに向こうが承知したのですから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:02.10,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019101,1022104}By the way, did Ayuhara Kozue-san join the club?{NOTE:ところで鮎原こずえさんは入部しましたか？}
