Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.52,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023314,1025525}I need the list of members by tomorrow.{NOTE:明日にでも入部届けを出してくださいね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:06.56,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025525,1026567}I understand.{NOTE:分かりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.69,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027693,1028694}Captain.{NOTE:キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.94,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029779,1031948}Professor Shimizu's attitude has changed.{NOTE:清水先生の態度は変わったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.74,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031948,1033741}Even though she was so indifferent before.{NOTE:あんなに無関心だったのにね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:18.28,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033741,1038287}She's motivated since we now have such a talent on the team.{NOTE:実力のありそうな人が入ってきたのでやる気を出したってところね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:20.37,Default,Suga,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038287,1040373}We won't get so much freedom anymore.{NOTE:今までみたいに自由がきかなくなるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.41,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040373,1041415}It'll be okay.{NOTE:大丈夫よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:23.58,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041415,1043584}We have nothing to worry about.{NOTE:あの二人だけではどうにもなりはしないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.34,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055179,1056347}Takeichi-san.{NOTE:武市さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.76,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056347,1057765}If Captain finds out…{NOTE:キャプテンに調べたら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.51,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059267,1060518}Takeichi-san!{NOTE:武市さん！}
