Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:47.52,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065189,1067525}Relax. It's our court, too, after all.{NOTE:いいじゃない？自分達のコート何だから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.48,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067525,1068484}Alright!{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:52.40,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070319,1072405}Huh, a respectable senior for once.{NOTE:え？話せる先輩。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:53.07,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072405,1073072}Oh?{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.36,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073072,1074365}Her too?{NOTE:XXX？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.99,Default,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075908,1077994}Let's clean up quickly so we can practice.{NOTE:さっさと掃除して練習しよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:18:00.66,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077994,1080663}That's what I'm talking about. I have to work hard!{NOTE:これは大変だ。頑張らなくちゃ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:03.33,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080663,1083332}Looks like we've brought some changes.{NOTE:私達の頑張りが効果上げたのよ。}
