Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086544,1087670}Let's not disappoint them.{NOTE:頑張ろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.42,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087670,1088421}Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
