Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.55,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095386,1096554}I'll help you out.{NOTE:来たわよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096554,1097847}Naka!{NOTE:ナカ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.93,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097847,1099932}In the end, I couldn't leave you, Chief.{NOTE:やっぱり親分について行こうと思ってね。}
