Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.07,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111277,1113070}Yeah. "Why would they want to play with us?!"{NOTE:それはまさかと思うわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.03,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1113070,1114030}Hahaha.{NOTE:—ははは。\\N—へへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:36.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115656,1116907}But we can't let our guard down.{NOTE:でも油断できないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116907,1119702}The captain's followers are gonna be here soon.{NOTE:巻き返しにでるわよ。あの人達。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:44.20,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121912,1124206}So, what do you think about it?{NOTE:で、あなた方の意見は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:47.20,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124206,1127209}They invited even more of their friends, which means…{NOTE:あの子たちが又仲間を増やしたってことは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:50.25,Default,Nakahara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127209,1130254}The future of our team doesn't look too bright.{NOTE:このままではバレー部の団結は崩されるわ。}
