Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:57.55,Default,Kanda,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135176,1137553}We need to get them under our control.{NOTE:何とか今のうちに手を打たないと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.18,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138471,1139180}I understand.{NOTE:分かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.76,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140264,1141766}That's what leadership is about.{NOTE:それが統率と言うものね。}
