Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:47.31,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183015,1187311}Submission is necessary to make the team work.{NOTE:チーム…チームワークを作る上に服従は必要です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:49.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187311,1189355}We're not your slaves.{NOTE:私達は奴隷じゃありません。}
