Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:23.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221303,1223723}If that's how you choose to see it.{NOTE:そう受け取っていただいても結構です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:25.72,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224682,1225725}Very well.{NOTE:いいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:29.06,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225725,1229061}Let's put you in the practice match\Nwith Misawa Academy.{NOTE:勝負は美沢学院との練習試合でつけてましょう。}
