Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:32.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231564,1232982}Fine.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:37.44,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232982,1237445}If you don't show your worth during that match… if you don't…!{NOTE:その試合で実力は伴わないと分かれば…その時は！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:38.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237445,1238446}I understand.{NOTE:分かっています。}
